            <h1 id="section-Authentication">Authentication</h1>
            <div class="section-list">
                <p>There are three ways to authenticate through Powerline API.</p>
                <h3>Bearer token (sent in an "Authorization" header)</h3>
                <p><code>curl -H "Authorization: Bearer TOKEN" https://api.powerli.ne</code></p>
                <h3><b style="color: white; background-color: red">Deprecated</b> Bearer token (sent in a "Token" header)</h3>
                <p><code>curl -H "Token: TOKEN" https://api.powerli.ne</code></p>
                <h3><b style="color: white; background-color: red">Deprecated</b> Bearer token (sent in an "Authorization" header with an additional user's type)</h3>
                <p><code>curl -H "Authorization: Bearer type='user' token='TOKEN'" https://api.powerli.ne</code></p>
            </div>
        </li>
        <li class="section active">
