            <h1 id="section-Schema">Schema</h1>
            <p class="section-list">
                All API access is over HTTPS, and accessed from the
                <code>{{ app.request.schemeAndHttpHost }}/api</code>.
                All data is received as JSON.
            </p>
            <p class="section-list">
                Blank fields are included as <code>null</code> instead of being omitted.
            </p>
